Package: roundrect
Title: Draw Rounded Rectangles with Independent Corner Radii
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Shahriar", "Siham", , "shahriar.siham@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a function to draw rounded rectangles with customizable, independent corner radii. 
    Unlike the default `grid` package's rounded rectangles, this allows setting different 
    radii for each corner. The function also features simplified parameter names for ease of use.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: 
    grid
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
